dct_description_sm: Shows oil and gas fields, pipelines and refineries; major gas processing plants, underground gas storage facilities, LPG storage, tanker terminals, oil refineries, LNG export plants and import terminals including those under construction or planned. Includes inset maps: Caspian Sea [Scale 1:4,550,000] -- Yamal [Scale 1:5,425,000] -- Northern Shakhalin Island [Scale 1:2,620,000] -- Middle Volga [Scale 1:4,000,000]. Includes energy and trade statistics and graphs. On verso: title panel and text.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
